race.description: Sportsbet Get On Extra Rating 0 - 56 Hcp
race.comment: Lots of these are making up the numbers. DE LUCA (7) resumed off a wide gate in a similar class and after a slow start race was pretty much over. At the tail and made late ground without threatening. Better than that and has placed 2/3 when second-up. Fitter and drawn to feature this time. TAINO ROCKET (2) resumes from a long break. Has won fresh and also won only try course and distance. Sure to be primed for a big return. SHADOWFAX (1) resumes and has good form for this. Resuming in an easier grade and is a fresh-up winner. Will give a sight. SUNDOGG (4) is another resuming and is also a fresh-up winner. Rates well on best but will need some luck from the poor draw.
